NAME
    MooseX::DeclareX::Privacy - shiny syntax for MooseX::Privacy

SYNOPSIS
            class Person extends Mammal
            {
                    private method decide ($choices) {
                            ...;
                    }
            }

DESCRIPTION
    This distribution adds three new plugins to MooseX::DeclareX.

    `private method`
        A method that can only be called from within this class.

    `protected method`
        A method that can be called from within this class, or from derived
        classes.

    `public method`
        Essentially a no-op.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs to
    <http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=MooseX-DeclareX-Privacy>.

SEE ALSO
    MooseX::DeclareX, MooseX::Privacy.

